{"about_the_game":"You have been assigned to this abandoned mental hospital by fate. This hospital has gone through very bad times, and your duty is to treat its highly challenging patients. But be careful, your sanity is at risk\u2026<br><br>Do not disturb the spirits of the former patients who have suffered greatly, but know that they will disturb you\u2026<br><br>In this adventure full of suspense, horror, and puzzles, you are not alone. Your assistant Sally will help you with everything\u2026<br><br>Every patient brings a new story and brand new puzzles\u2026<br><br><br>GAME FEATURES:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> A puzzle game filled with elements of mystery and suspense.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> An immersive atmosphere. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> Includes dialogues, but most things are conveyed visually in a universally understandable way.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> Enter the patient's mind, solve complexities, and heal the patients.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> Contains more than 20 puzzles and mini-games.<br><br>Note: The game contains elements of violence and suspense. <br><br>With &quot;Transmorphosis,&quot; the first game that reflects Bottle Bottom Games' drawing and gameplay style, Bottle Bottom Games aims to bring a new vision to hand-crafted indie puzzle games with a cinematic perspective. We hope you enjoy and love our game as much as we do.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138580/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736958951","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138580/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736958951","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138580/cfdd819139a78b9e7ba40fabf9e948bfa727c394/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736958951","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138580/cfdd819139a78b9e7ba40fabf9e9